It's really good to see you
again, and Mr. Spellman.

00:36:26.310 --> 00:36:31.250 position:56%
You were talking about poetry and
music I mean it's always been there.

00:36:31.250 --> 00:36:35.570
If you go to the Greek tragedies,
you know, the choruses and,

00:36:35.570 --> 00:36:39.870
