or your writing?

00:36:57.010 --> 00:36:59.650
Has there been any
cross pollination there.

00:36:59.650 --> 00:37:00.950
&gt;&gt; Joy Harjo: Definitely.

00:37:00.950 --> 00:37:02.250
I think it's in America.

00:37:02.250 --> 00:37:06.060 position:56%
I think it was there at Congo Square
when our people were, you know,

00:37:06.060 --> 00:37:07.360
