think the African people then

00:37:09.970 --> 00:37:12.820
like our tribes here
everybody knew their identity,

00:37:12.820 --> 00:37:16.330
still had their tribal identities
and so I can see what went on.

00:37:16.330 --> 00:37:18.080
It was a crossover too.

00:37:18.080 --> 00:37:19.570
It didn't just go one way.

00:37:19.570 --> 00:37:24.010
There is no one way land bridge
that Natives came across, you know.

00:37:24.010 --> 00:37:28.990
