which wouldn't you like to have

00:39:26.330 --> 00:39:27.690
that with you on the stage?

00:39:27.690 --> 00:39:30.030
And so that's always been there.

00:39:30.030 --> 00:39:34.350
He also wrote with
Kurt Vile and so forth.

00:39:34.350 --> 00:39:37.630
So, that's always been
an element of the music.

00:39:37.630 --> 00:39:40.220
There's nothing new actually.

00:39:40.220 --> 00:39:46.170
It all was an expression of
tendencies that have been in art

00:39:46.170 --> 00:39:48.360
from the beginning and so people

00:39:48.360 --> 00:39:50.930
like Jayne Cortez was the
first musician I knew who,

00:39:50.930 --> 00:39:52.560
